server.cpp
- accepts directional commands from client.cpp
- sends commands to arduino
- connect to arduino (line of code requiring connection to arduino commented out for testing purposes)
- to make, type 'make server'
- to run, type './server.out'

client.cpp
- connects to server.cpp &
- sends directional commands
- to make, type 'make client'
- to run, type './client.out'


CONTROL INSTRUCTIONS:

s - Stop			r - turn Right		u - speed Up
f - Forward			l - turn Left		d - slow Down
